 
<p>

The wrecker made a plan, called "Schedule F", to enable him to
<a href="https://www.commondreams.org/news/2022/07/22/authoritarianism-101-trump-plot-purge-civil-servants-if-reelected-draws-alarm">arbitrarily purge the employees</a> in 50,000 federal civil service jobs
and replace them with people personally loyal to him.  This could corrupt
the whole federal bureaucracy.
<p>
Any Republican elected in 2024 might put this into practice.
Reportedly Republicans in the Senate support that plan, and will block
the efforts to legislate against it.

 